<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Eloheh Health — Testimonials</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    body{font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;margin:24px;color:#2b2f33}
    h1{color:#0D3B66;margin:0 0 6px}
    .lead{font-family:Georgia,serif;color:#6E7681;font-size:1.05rem}
    blockquote{font-style:italic;border-left:4px solid #1E90A0;padding-left:12px;color:#555}
    .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-top:14px}
    .card{border:1px solid #E6EAF0;border-radius:12px;padding:12px;background:#fff}
    img{width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #E6EAF0;margin-bottom:8px}
    ul,ol{margin-left:20px}
    .btn{display:inline-block;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #0D3B66;color:#fff;background:#0D3B66;text-decoration:none}
    .btn.secondary{background:#fff;color:#0D3B66;border-color:#1E90A0}
    footer{margin-top:18px;font-size:.9rem;color:#6E7681}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Customer Testimonials</h1>
  <p class="lead"><em>Real outcomes from members and providers.</em></p>

  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="assets/patient1.jpg" alt="Member story">
      <blockquote>“With the alerts, I avoided an ER visit. The nurse checked on me within minutes.” — J.D., member</blockquote>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <img src="assets/clinic1.jpg" alt="Clinic partner">
      <blockquote>“Readmissions dropped 14% in our CHF cohort over the pilot.” — M.G., clinic director</blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 style="color:#0D3B66;margin-top:16px">Common themes</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Members feel supported between visits</li>
    <li>Clinics act sooner with trend flags</li>
    <li>Clear ROI from avoided admissions</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 style="color:#0D3B66">How we collect feedback</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Post-enrollment surveys (30/90 days)</li>
    <li>Quarterly provider interviews</li>
    <li>Annual outcomes review with finance</li>
  </ol>

  <!-- Links (≤3): download, external, contact -->
  <p><a class="btn" href="assets/Eloheh_Case_Studies.pdf" download>Download case studies (PDF)</a></p>
  <p><a class="btn secondary" href="https://www.ahrq.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AHRQ patient safety</a></p>
  <p><a class="btn" href="mailto:firstname.lastname@purdue.edu?subject=Testimonials%20page">Contact me</a></p>

  <footer><em>Last modified:</em> <span id="lastModified"></span></footer>
  <script>document.getElementById('lastModified').textContent = document.lastModified;</script>
</body>
</html>
